<div class="section">
  <div class="section__inner">
    <div class= "container">
      <div class="tabs">
        <div class="tabs__header">
          <div class="tabs__title">
            <h2>Please select one font</h2>
          </div>
          <ul id="tabs" class="tabs__nav">
            <li class="active">
              <a href="#tab1">My fonts</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#tab2">By my fonts</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="tabs__content">
          <div class="tabs__pane active" id="tab1">
            <!--<form>-->
            <div class="grid grid--gutter">
              <div class="grid__col grid__col-5@small grid__col-12@xsmall">
                {% include '../card/_card.twig' with {
                    'card__id': 'merriweather',
                    'card__value': 'merriweather',
                    'card_letter': 'M',
                    'card__label': 'Merriweather project is ked by Sorkin Type',
                  } only
                %}
              </div>
              <div class="grid__col grid__col-7@small grid__col-12@xsmall">
                {% include '../card/_card.twig' with {
                    'modifier_class': 'card--horizontal',
                    'card__color': 'pink',
                    'card__id': 'roboto',
                    'card__value': 'roboto',
                    'card_letter': 'R',
                    'card__label': 'Roboto project is ked by Sorkin Type',
                  } only
                %}

                {% include '../card/_card.twig' with {
                    'modifier_class': 'card--horizontal',
                    'card__color': 'blue',
                    'card__id': 'nano-sans',
                    'card__value': 'nano-sans',
                    'card_letter': 'NS',
                    'card__label': 'Nano Sans project is ked by Sorkin Type',
                  } only
                %}
              </div>
            </div>
            <!--</form>-->
          </div>
          <div class="tabs__pane" id="tab2">
            <p class="centered">
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Proin luctus ipsum dictum, lacinia nisl auctor, aliquam lacus.
              Curabitur venenatis nisl vitae nibh pretium ultricies. Integer lobortis semper est, vitae ultricies odio mattis non.
              Maecenas elementum vestibulum bibendum. Maecenas dapibus eleifend mauris et gravida.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>